snippet.title: Rakka Rakka - Video Song | Bandra | Dileep, Tamannaah | Sam C.S | Shankar Mahadevan, Nakshathra
snippet.description:
For more latest songs & videos, subscribe 👉 https://bit.ly/Saregama_Malayalam

Presenting the sizzling first single - "Rakka Rakka" video song from 'Bandra' ft. Dileep, Tamannaah. Directed by Arun Gopy. A Sam C.S musical!

Song Credits:-
Rakka Rakka
Song Composed and Arranged by - Sam C.S 
Singer : Shankar Mahadevan, Nakshathra Santhosh
Lyrics: Vinayak Sasikumar
Programmed by - Onasis Mohan 
Guitar(Bass, Electric, acoustic) : Joseph vijay 
Shenoy: Balesh
Flute : Kiran
Rhythms and Percussions :  Kalyan, Prithvi Raj 
Backing Vocals: Velu, Abishek Ar, CD Anbumani, S Aakash Edwin 
Recording Engineer : CD Anbumani , Abishek Ar, Aakash Edwin @ Psalter Record Inn Pvt Ltd Chennai.
Ameya Mategaonkar @ Lambodara Studios, Mumbai
Arjun B Nair @ Sonic Island studios Kochi.
Amal Mithu @ MLounge Studio Kochi
Mixing & Mastering: Balu Thankachan @ 20db black Studio.
Assisted by Paul Daniel and Hariharan
Music Production Manager: K Mahima Chowdhary
Music Incharge : Velavan B 
Music Co-ordinator: Kannan
Music Production Team : Indhumathi, Sathyamurthy
Tech support: Parthiban @pro audio

Movie Credits:-
Directed by Arun Gopy 
Produced By Vinayaka Ajith
Starring: Dileep, Tamannaah Bhatia, Dino Morea, Lena, Mamtha Mohandas, Kalabhavan Shajon, Sarath Kumar, Rajveer Ankur Singh, Dara Singh Khurana, Amit Tiwari, Easwari Rao, etc.
Production: Ajith Vinayaka Films Pvt Ltd
Written by: Udaykrishna
DOP: Shaji Kumar
Editor: Vivek Harshan
Music Composed and Arranged by: Sam CS
Programmed by - Onasis Mohan, CD Anbumani 
Backing Vocals - Sam CS, Abishek Ar
Guitar - (Bass, Electric, acoustic) - Joseph Vijay 
Strings & Brass - Chennai Orchestra 
Recording Engineer : CD Anbumani ,Abishek Ar, 
S Aakash Edwin@ Psalter Record Inn Pvt Ltd Chennai.  
Music Production Manager: K Mahima Chowdhary
Mixing & Mastering: Balu Thankachan at 20dB black Studio.
Assisted by Paul Daniel and Hariharan
Production management Team : Kannan M , Indhumathi, Sathya Murthy 
Music co-ordinator : Velavan B
Mixing: Fortune Studios-Ajith A George 
Action Director: Anbariv
Choreographer: Prasanna Master, Dinesh Master
Production Designer: Subhash Karun
Chief Associate Director: Ratheesh Palode
Costume Designer: Praveen Varma
Makeup: Ranjith Ambady
Sound Design: Renganaath Ravee
DI: Lixo Pixels
Stills: Ramdas Mathur
Designs: Anand Rajendran
PRO: Sabari
Distribution: Ajith Vinayaka Release
VFX: Baywood & Meraki VFX

Lyrics:-
Rakka Rakka 

Female:
Oh manikuruvi 
Mehalkuruvi
Man ki rani…

En manimaaran 
Magadeeran 
Raajavaaroo

Rajakulathin 
Kodiparakkum
Malvaatheril 

Noorazhakodi-
Nnavan enne 
Kaanan vanno 

Male:
Nee madhura punchirikaari 
Enn maayavaani 
Yavana sundhari tholkkum 
Enn vaazhvin devi 

Vala thilangana kayyil 
Kayycherthe ninne 
Vara sumangaliaaki 
Njan konde pokum 

Rau Rau Ra Rakkaa Rakkaa
Rau Rau Ra Rakkaa Rakkaa
Rau Rau Ra Rakkaa Rakkaa
Rau Rau Ra Rakkaa Rakkaa

Female:
Aanveeran thottal pookum 
Aaromal Pennaanenne 
Mevaarin aramanayum njanum 
Ninn swantham…

(Rakka Rakka)

Female:
Raavirullunnu…
Vazhipaatha mangunnu…
Ivale kavaraan aararum 
Vannaalo…

Male:
Ethu sulthaanum 
Padakootti vannotte …
Udalvaalthala than 
Choodaale ninne njan 
Kaakkoole…

Female:
Nenjillu nenjillu neeyalle 
Mundhiya munthiri thenalle 
Ennile ennilu vannaal njan 
Veenjaay thoovaam…

Male:
Ponmani kothiya pallakkil 
Munnilananja nilaavalle 
Kallupathichoru koolaarin 
Ponnalle 

Kannalle…

Chorus:
Rau Rau Ra Rakkaa Rakkaa
Rau Rau Ra Rakkaa Rakkaa
Rau Rau Ra Rakkaa Rakkaa
Rau Rau Ra Rakkaa Rakkaa

Female:
Kannaalan kayyaal thottaal 
Poopookkum 
Pennaanenne…

Mevaarin aramanayum njanum 
Ninn swantham…

(Rakka Rakka)

Label: Saregama India Limited, A RPSG Group Company

We made Hot and Sweet chicken sauce by using Honey and Poprica. Before adding sauce, the chicken wings are so crispy then it is tasty!

snippet.title: Leo Post-release Lokesh Kanagaraj Interview with Sudhir Srinivasan | Leo | Vijay | Trisha | Part 1
snippet.description:
In this spoiler-filled interaction with Sudhir Srinivasan, #LokeshKanagaraj talks about all things #Leo, envisioning #Vijay in the LCU, and more 

This is the first part of the interaction.   #CinemaExpress 

00:10 - 01:45  - Loki and The Kerala Story
01:46 - 02:45 - How did Loki respond to the polarising responses 
02:46 - 04:40 - How did Loki accept the criticism about the flashback
04:41 - 08.40 - How Loki fixed the duration of Leo
08:41 - 09:40 - What does Loki believe is the truth of Leo?  
09:41 - 10:54  - What is Loki's favourite thing about the Leo flashback
10:55 - 12:00 - Is Loki really constrained by fans 
12:01 - 16:16 - What does it take for young directors like Loki to work with superstars
16:17 - 20:40 - How does Loki see the audience's fixation on box-office numbers
20:41 - 24:38 - Who does Loki think is the villain of Leo? 
24:39 - 25:43 - Loki opens about the Hulk Connect in Leo
25:44 - 28:56 - Is Leo a good person or a bad person? 
28:57 - 32.30 - Is Loki glorifying the bad guy in Leo? 
32:31 - 32:56 - What is Parthiban's take on a drug-free society? 
32:57 - 33.24 - Does Loki really think the twin angle worked in favour of the film? 
33:25 - 37:58 - How does Loki work with his writing room? 
37:59 - 42:05 - Does Loki feel the pressure of casting the big names
42:06 - 50:00 - The big question of Loki and LCU
Follow us on

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/XpressCinema/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/XpressCinema
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/xpresscinema/

For more film news, interviews and reviews, go to: http://www.cinemaexpress.com

Cinema Express is a wing of The New Indian Express, and gives you the latest in the world of cinema, with special emphasis on South India, and particular distaste for gossip. The New Indian Express is published by Express Publications (Madurai) Limited from 25 centres in Tamil Nadu, Karnataka, Andhra Pradesh, Kerala and Odisha.
The company also publishes the Tamil daily, Dinamani, Cinema Express (Tamil), Malayalam Varika (Malayalam), Sakhi (Kannada), and Sunday Standard from New Delhi.

snippet.title: PART 2 Leo Post-release Lokesh Kanagaraj Interview with Sudhir Srinivasan | Leo | Vijay | Trisha
snippet.description:
In this spoiler-filled interaction with Sudhir Srinivasan, #LokeshKanagaraj talks about all things #Leo, bringing #Vijay into the LCU, and more 

This is the SECOND part of the interaction

00:00 - 5:22 - Including History of Violence, what are the other inspirations in Loki's films

05:23 - 07:00 - How did Loki sketch the husband-wife equation in Leo

07:01 - 09:44 - How did the hyena come into the Loki Universe

09:45 - 12:08 - What does Loki think of how people connect the hyena metaphor and other layers of Leo 

12:09 - 14:23 - What elevated Loki's cinematic knowledge

14:24 - 17:48 - What does Loki think of the audience understanding? 

17:49 - 19:37 - What are the plans for the hyena in the LCU? 

19:38 - 20:49 - Will Loki attempt the horror genre? 

20:50 - 23.58 - How does Loki zero in on the retro songs in his films? 

23:59 - 26:16 - How does Loki create an atmosphere for usage of these songs? 

26:17 - 27:20 - What inspired Loki to make that badass Vijay intro card?

27:21 - 28:11 - Why does Loki believe second time is the charm? 

28:12 - 28:38 - Loki on finally bringing Mansoor Ali Khan into the LCU

28:39 - 29:57 - What were the steps Loki took to ensure Parthiban's body adapted to the war scars?
 
29:58 - 32:16 - How important is Anirudh to Loki's films? 

32:17 - 34:27 - What were the various contributions of Anirudh to LEO? 

34:28 - 36:14 - How does Loki work with Anbariv to get the fight choreography on point in Leo? 

36:15 - 37:35 - Does Loki think that the stunts got a bit generic in certain scenes in the second half? 

37:36 - 39:24 - What was the most satisfying response Loki got post the release of Leo? What was his biggest takeaway? 

39:25 - 41:10 - Loki opens up on the LCU Routemap
 
41:11 - 43:23 - Loki signs off by talking about his next biggie,  Thalaivar 171

snippet.title: Emiway x Savlon Swasth India – HAATH DHONA COOL HAI #HandwashLegend ft. The Dharavi Dream Project
snippet.description:
This Iconic Hip-Hop move 👏🏼 is now the HANDWASHING Move!
Now after the hack, comes the track!

The track aims to make washing hands with Handwash or Soap cool in the minds of children, keeping them healthy and safe from various illnesses.

Let’s all wash our hands and become a #HandwashLegend.
___

ITC's Savlon Swasth India Mission - one of the largest school programmes of its kind, is committed to seeding hand hygiene habits in over 85 lakh school children, through continuous awareness and engagement activities.  
___

The Dharavi Dream Project After School of Hip-Hop is a non-profit organisation based in Mumbai. Through various educational programmes, mentorships and community engagement initiatives, it supports children living in Dharavi, Mumbai which today is known for its culturally vibrant hip-hop talent.

#HandwashingForAll #SavlonSwasthIndiaMission
___

Audio Credits:
Song :- HAATH DHONA COOL HAI 
Artist / Lyrics : EmiwayBantai
Prod by : Emiway Bantai 
Mix & mastered by :- Emiway bantai

snippet.title: १ किलो चकली भाजणी | तांदूळ कोणता? काटेरी, कमी तेलकट चकलीसाठी या 10 चुका टाळा | 1 Kilo Chakli Bhajani
snippet.description:

 1. सर्व प्रकारची लाकडी घाणा तेलं | All Types of Wood Pressed Oils
 2. डंकावर कुटून केलेला कांदा लसूण मसाला | Handmade Kanda Lasun Masala
 3. सरिताज किचन सेंद्रिय गुळ | Chemical free Jaggery cubes and powder 
 4. सेंधव मीठ | Pink Himalayan Salt
 5. सेंद्रियहळद | Organic Turmeric

१ किलो चकली भाजणी | तांदूळ कोणता? काटेरी, कमी तेलकट चकलीसाठी या 10 चुका टाळा | 1 Kilo Chakli Bhajani

रेशनच्या तांदळाची चकली भाजणी व चकली 
चकली रेसिपी | कुरकुरीत चकली रेसिपी | दिवाळी स्पेशल | दिवाळी सणासाठी खास भाजणी व चकली रेसिपी | भाजणीची चकली | पारंपरिक चकली रेसिपी | चकली रेसिपी मराठी | महाराष्ट्रीयन दिवाळी फराळ | Chakali Recipe | Crispy Chakali Recipe | Diwali Special | For Diwali Special Bhajani and Chakali Recipe | Bhajanichi Chakali Recipe | Traditional Chakali Recipe | Chakali Recipe Marathi | Maharashtrian Diwali Faral | 
साहित्य | Ingredients  
भाजणी साठी | To make Bhajani 
वजनी प्रमाण | Gram Measurements 
 • रेशन तांदूळ | Ration Rice 600 gram 
 • डाळवे | Dalave 200 gram
 • मूग डाळ | Mug Dal 125 gram
 • उडीद डाळ | Udid  Dal 75 gram  
 • पोहे | Pohe 50 gram
 • धने | Coriander Seeds 20 gram
 • जिरे | Cumin 20 gram
 • साबुदाणा | Sabudana 50 gram 
वाटीचे प्रमाण | Cup Measurements  
 • रेशन तांदूळ 3 Cup | Ration Rice 3 Cups
 • डाळवे पावणे दोन कप | Dalave 1 Cup & 3/4 cup
 • मूग डाळ पाऊण कप | Mug Dal 3/4 cup
 • उडीद डाळ अर्धा कप | Udid  Dal 1/2 cup
 • पोहे 1 कप | Pohe 50 gram 1 Cup
 • धने पाव कप | Coriander Seeds 1/4 Cup
 • जिरे २ मोठे चमचे | Cumin 2 TBSP
 • साबुदाणा पाव कप | Sabudana 1/4 cup

भाजणी पासून चकली | To make Bhajani chakali 
 • तयार भाजणी ४ वाट्या  |  Ready Bhajani 4 cup 
 • उकळते पाणी ३ वाट्या  |  Boil Water 3 cup 
 • मीठ 1.5 चमचा | Salt 1.5 tsp 
 • तीळ ३ चमचे  |  Sesame 3 tsp 
 • ओवा ½ चमचा | Ajwain ½ tsp 
 • मिरची पावडर १ मोठा चमचा | Red Chilly Powder 1 tbsp 
 • तेलाचे मोहन 4 चमचे | Oil Mohan 4 tsp 

To make Bhajani 
To make Chakali 

Other Recipes 

1/2 किलो मैदयाची बिस्कीटांपेक्षा खुसखुशीत गोड शंकरपाळी लेयर्सवाली| 1 Kilo Shankarpali Recipe marathi
https://youtu.be/bRFdQ_j-tU0?si=07KqRvvupGAcjnfY

1/2 किलो प्रमाणात करा किंवा कसेही तेलाचे मोहन/सोडा न वापरता कमी तेलकट कुरकुरीत चटपटीत मसाला शेव
https://youtu.be/Wt9yp5Ppagc?si=aBJO4YV5xvL4w2Z5

1 kg पातळ पोह्यांचा चिवडा। चिवडा नरम,चिवट होतो? या 7 टिप्स वापरून, महिनाभर कुरकुरीत राहणारा चिवडा
https://youtu.be/FFH97R1IhIQ?si=GacetpecuYPM1FU6

1/2 किलो तांदूळ घ्या किंवा कसेही, गूळाचे योग्य प्रमाण घेऊन जाळीदार/ बिस्किटांपेक्षा खुसखुशीत अनारसे
https://youtu.be/Y-sskfJ83-A?si=eR-e-ypXVMHU7seJ

दिवाळी फराळ, 1 किलो खुसखुशीत पाकळी चिरोटे/ खाजा। भरपूर पदर सुटलेले सुंदर पाकळीच्या आकाराचे चिरोटे
https://youtu.be/pDX9sCOQBcg?si=i5NNt3FwY_VtU3EH

जिभेवर ठेवताच विरघळणारी, पडदे/लेयरस असलेली खुसखुशीत बालुशाही।तोंडात विरघळणारी बालुशाही। Balushahi 
https://youtu.be/Q-qWvLPvFwo?si=GxfJplF5mE9RqZ4z

लगेच समजेल अशा पद्धतीने बनवा साठा न लावता खुसखुशीत करंजी, लवकर मऊ होणार नाही l karanji / gujiya
https://youtu.be/k6HiPQlhJlQ?si=BwNKw3b_VTX-1zHu

रवा-बेसन भाजण्याचे झंझट नकोय? अनोख्या पद्धतीने बनवा दाणेदार खुसखुशीत रवा बेसन लाडू | rava besan ladu
https://youtu.be/o_v98uJ0GP0?si=BX7c7knu_VDFRJT9

snippet.title: Minecraft CHICKEN vs HUNTER
snippet.description:
Minecraft CHICKEN vs HUNTER... I have to take a CHICKEN to beat the ender dragon. My friend has to stop me. Should be easy right?

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @dream
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dream

George: @GeorgeNotFound 

This video is a different Minecraft challenge concept that we have never done before! It's similar to Minecraft Manhunt, in that I have to beat the game while George tries to hunt the CHICKEN, instead of me. The chicken heals over time like a player, and has 20 hearts.

It's a race, and it's super intense and we had a lot of laughs. I love doing these challenges.

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin

#MinecraftChallenge

localized.title: Minecraft CHICKEN vs HUNTER
localized.description:
Minecraft CHICKEN vs HUNTER... I have to take a CHICKEN to beat the ender dragon. My friend has to stop me. Should be easy right?

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @dream
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dream

George: @GeorgeNotFound 

This video is a different Minecraft challenge concept that we have never done before! It's similar to Minecraft Manhunt, in that I have to beat the game while George tries to hunt the CHICKEN, instead of me. The chicken heals over time like a player, and has 20 hearts.

It's a race, and it's super intense and we had a lot of laughs. I love doing these challenges.

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin

#MinecraftChallenge

Episode 3916: The Perfect Gift
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha apologizes to Babita for the present misunderstanding. Jetha also asks Babita to assist him in selecting an acceptable gift for his client, who is Bengali like her. Babita first hesitates, wondering how she could choose a present for someone she has never met. Later, she says that, in her opinion, sweets are a great way to win any Bengali's heart. Jetha expressly asks Babits' preference, and she responds that any Moon-related present would be her favorite. Jetha runs to Taarak for assistance. What is Jetha going to do now?

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.description:

 3. सरिताज किचन सेंद्रिय गुळ | Chemical free Jaggery cubes and powder 
 4. सेंधव मीठ | Pink Himalayan Salt

दिवाळी तयारी करताना 10 या चुका टाळा | दिवाळी तयारीच्या 10 टिप्स / 10 Useful Diwali Kitchen Tips

दिवाळी तयारी 
आज आपण सरितास किचन मध्ये दिवाळीची तयारी कशी करावी हे बघणार आहोत. सगळीकडे दिवाळीची लगबग सुरु होते.  घरोघरी स्वच्छता व साफसफाई केली जाते. घर सजवले जाते. साफसफाई करिता काही टिप्स सांगण्याचा प्रयत्न करत आहे.  लहान मुलांपासून ते मोठ्यांच्या सगळ्यांच्या जिव्हाळ्याचा व उत्साहाचा विषय म्हणजे दिवाळी शॉपिंग. यासाठी शॉपिंग कशी करावी. यामध्ये रांगोळी व रंगांची खरेदी, सामान खरेदी, रोषणाईसाठी कंदील खरेदी, लाईटचे तोरण खरेदी, पणत्या खरेदी, फुले व  फुलांच्या माळा व तोरण खरेदी, पर्यावरण पूरक फटाके खरेदी  हे सर्व बघणार आहोत. घरोघरी पदार्थांची रेलचेल सुरु होते. लाडू, चकली, चिवडा, करंजी, अनारसे, चिरोटे, स्वीट रेसिपी, मोहनथाळ अशे बरेच पदार्थ बनवले जातात.
सगळीकडे रोषणाई केली जाते. प्रचंड उत्साहात वसूबारस, धनत्रयोदशी, नरक चतुर्थी, लक्ष्मी पूजन व भाऊबीज साजरा केला जातो. त्याकरिता रोज नवनवीन पदार्थ बनवून देवाला नैवेद्य अर्पण केला जातो.  लहान मुलांपासून मोठ्यांपर्यंत सर्व जण फटाके उडवून आनंद साजरा करतात.   
दिवाळी फराळ स्वादिष्ट व उत्तम होण्यासाठी दिवाळी फराळ कसा करावा यासाठी दिवाळी फराळ रेसिपी व ते बनवण्या साठी  लागणारे सर्व साहित्य व प्रमाण, योग्य टिप्स सर्व थोडक्यात सांगण्याचा प्रयत्न केला आहे की जेणेकरून नवशिक्यांनाही न चुकता प्रत्येक पदार्थ परफेक्ट बनवता येईल.

Other Links 
1/2 किलो प्रमाणात करा किंवा कसेही/यंदा दिवाळी फराळ बिघडणार नाही, आत्मविश्वासाने बनवा पर्फेक्ट पदार्थ
https://youtu.be/YPvGL1l1QZg?si=tn1rCmCoeEDQXArh

1 kg पातळ पोह्यांचा चिवडा। चिवडा नरम, चिवट होतो? या 7 टिप्स वापरून, महिनाभर कुरकुरीत राहणारा चिवडा
https://youtu.be/FFH97R1IhIQ?si=U3Psk69RIU8-7Nli

½ किलो रव्याची खुसखुशीत करंजी |मऊ पडू नये, तेलकट होऊ नये म्हणून या 5 टिप्स | 1 Kilo Karanji Recipe
https://youtu.be/SDPQV21yroU?si=u94ML68rWaB_wYGm

या 7 टिप्स वापरून बनवा 1kg चकली पारंपरिक भाजणी आणि तेलकट न होणारी पोकळ कुरकुरीत चकली। भाजणीची चकली
https://youtu.be/ij4krqmchXM?si=NsiTT3JRGNlCyVpp

1/2 किलो मैदयाची बिस्कीटांपेक्षा खुसखुशीत गोड शंकरपाळी लेयर्सवाली| 1 Kilo Shankarpali Recipe marathi
https://youtu.be/bRFdQ_j-tU0?si=anYkWwauTs0h1LJW

दिवाळीसाठी 1 कप बेसनाचे ½Kg मोतीचूर लाडू| मार्केटसारखा मोतीचूर बनवण्याची परफेक्ट रेसिपी MotichurLadu
https://youtu.be/RnexeXfdfsA?si=kYSAP5eyapzm2LCW

बेसनाचे तुपाचे परफेक्ट प्रमाण घेऊन, खुसखुशीत, दाणेदार मोहनथाळ /बेसन बर्फी। Mohanthal /दिवाळी फराळ 10
https://youtu.be/K-VQTuHyFv4?si=76eVD1dB6N8jDpF6


Preparation for Diwali. 

The festive season has begun. Diwali the biggest celebrated festival by Indians is around the corner.  There is loads of preparation that needs to be done for Diwali. Right from cleaning house, shopping for groceries, cloths, decorative items, items related to rituals , buying gifts for friends & relatives etc. Managing diwali preparation along with routine life becomes difficulty.   
Are you thinking where to start from. Don’t worry. Saritas Kitchen is here with 10 daily & useful Kitchen tips, which will help you think, plan & organise your diwali house cleaning, shopping of groceries for making sweets, namkeens, faral, etc. along with that it will help you to decide on what type of decoration you can do to decorate your house.

Directed by Masato Inui
Starring Bhuvan Bam, Beat Takeshi, Osamu Shitara (BANANAMAN), Yuki Himura (BANANAMAN), Shinya Ueda (CREAM STEW), Naomi Watanabe, Ennosuke Ichikawa, Hayato Tani, Subaru Kimura.

Official Release Date November 2, 2023 on Prime Video.

About:
Bhuvan Bam lends his distinctive voice and unique humor as commentator in the brand-new season of Takeshi's Castle. Classic games are making a comeback with new and terrifying obstacles emerging one after another. The lord of the castle, Beat Takeshi, entrusts Bananaman to protect it. Subaru Kimura is the attack force’s new leader. The elite team gathers to bring down the revived Takeshi’s Castle.

About Prime Video: Prime Video is a premium streaming service that offers Prime members a collection of award-winning Amazon Original series, thousands of movies & TV shows—all with the ease of finding what they love to watch in one place. Prime Video is just one of the many benefits of a Prime membership, available for just ₹1499/ year. 
Included with Prime Video: Thousands of acclaimed TV shows & movies across languages & geographies, including Indian films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, and HOME, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Farzi, Jubilee, Dahaad, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Made in Heaven, Four More Shots Please!, Mumbai Diaries 26/11, Suzhal – The Vortex, Modern Love, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Guilty Minds, Cinema Marte Dum Tak, and Amazon Original movies like Maja Ma & Ammu. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video’s exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ₹599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.
Enhanced experiences: Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- & High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies & TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing. 
Video Entertainment Marketplace: In addition to a Prime Video subscription, customers can also purchase add-on subscriptions to other streaming services, as well as, get rental access to movies on Prime Video. Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination – Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent – no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting primevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

A haunting incident takes place with two men, as soon as they entered inside a strange house. Now, Stay Tuned to know how will CID officers investigate about the case and get the hidden facts about the whole incident.

Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman

Episode: 1180

#CID #सीआईडी #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #LatestCID

About CID:
-----------------
Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.title: Barcelona 1-2 Real Madrid | HIGHLIGHTS | LaLiga 2023/24
snippet.description:
Real Madrid came from behind to win a thrilling Clásico after Gündoğan's goal had put Barca ahead at half-time, but Bellingham turned the game around in a superb second half. He equalised in the 68th minute with a spectacular strike from outside the area and then sealed all three points for the leaders in stoppage time, latching on to Modrić's ball inside the six-yard box. Our team is now four points clear of Barcelona.
#ElClásico | #LaLigaHighlights

es.title: Barcelona 1-2 Real Madrid | RESUMEN | LaLiga 2023/24
es.description:
El Real Madrid se llevó un emocionante Clásico. Tocó remontar el gol de Gündoğan con el que el Barcelona se marchó al descanso, pero apareció Bellingham para dar la vuelta al encuentro en una soberbia segunda mitad. Empató en el 68’ con un espectacular disparo desde fuera del área y dio los tres puntos al líder en el añadido, al aprovechar un balón de Modrić en el área pequeña. Nuestro equipo suma y sigue y ya distancia en cuatro puntos al Barcelona.
#ElClásico | #LaLigaHighlights

ar.description:
قدم ريال مدريد كلاسيكو مثير بعد أن سجل برشلونة في الدقائق الأولى عن طريق جوندوجان في الشوط الأول، لكن بيلينجهام قلب المباراة رأسًا على عقب في الشوط الثاني، وأدرك التعادل في الدقيقة 68 بتسديدة مذهلة من خارج منطقة الجزاء ثم حسم النقاط الثلاث للمتصدر في الوقت المحتسب بدل الضائع، بعد ضربة حاسمة من مودريتش. فريقنا الآن يتقدم بفارق أربع نقاط عن برشلونة.
